::Prowl/Dark One/Nemesis Enforcer::

Prowl rounds another corner, hoping Dinobot was still behind him. He stops at 
a door. "I think this is it," he says into his silencer, "But going through 
the door would be suicide."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Dark One turns around. "Its finished," he tosses the bug to Nemesis, who 
barely catches it.

Nemesis Enforcer growls at Dark One, then turning to Iron Raptor. "Now, my 
dear girl, who should we start on first?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
"Its finished."

"Now, my dear girl, who should we start on first?"

Prowl's head jerks up from where the sound came from. Above him was a fairly 
big vent. He frowns. Why would the Alliance put a vent this size in the 
tortrue chambers.

Of course! They'd want the screams to be heard through the base.

"Up there," Prowl says into his silencer, pointing to the cealing, "That's 
our way in. Give me a lift."

The cealing was too high for either him or Dinobot to reach alone, but if 
Dinobot boosted him up, he would be able to pull the fellow Maximal up too.
